slazzer.com/api - An AI powered API to remove backgrounds from images

crontab.cronhub.io - A tool to workout out cron syntax, so you con‚Äôt have to

namae.dev - Check all the nooks and crannies of the web for that new name you want to use

flaticon.com - Icons, lots and lots of icons also look at (materialdesignicons.com nom package)

regex101.com - Regular expression tester with syntax highlighting, explanation, cheat sheet
